Package: TruncComp2
Type: Package
Title: Two-sample comparison of truncated continuous outcome by parametric or semi-parametric maximum likelihood
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Andreas Kryger Jensen
Maintainer: Andreas Kryger Jensen <aeje@sund.ku.dk>
Description: Implements likelihood-ratio methods for comparing two groups when
    a continuous outcome has a distinguished atom value representing an
    unobserved or undefined outcome. The package provides both a fully
    parametric approach and a semi-parametric approach based on an internal
    empirical-likelihood routine for the observed-outcome mean difference.
